'''三過氧化三丙酮'''（{{lang-en|Triacetone triperoxide}}，[[简称|简称]]'''TATP'''）或'''過氧化三環丙酮'''，[[俗稱|俗稱]]'''撒旦之母'''，是一種[[有機過氧化物|有機過氧化物]][[起爆藥|起爆藥]]及[[二甲基过氧化酮|二甲基过氧化酮]]的閉環[[三聚體|三聚體]]，起爆力介於[[雷汞|雷汞]]與[[疊氮化鉛|疊氮化鉛]]之間。嗅若[[丙酮|丙酮]]的[[白色|白色]]細膩[[晶體|晶體]]，不溶於水，但溶於[[氯仿|氯仿]]等[[有機溶劑|有機溶劑]]。

曾考慮用作[[雷管|雷管]][[裝藥|裝藥]]，但因其易於[[昇華|昇華]]的特性（於室溫放置兩週，質量損失可達66%<ref>Viacheslav Egorshev, Valery Sinditskii, Sergei Smirnov, et al. A comparative study on cyclic acetone peroxides[C]//New Trends in Research of Energetic Materials. Czech Republic, 2009: 113 – 123.</ref>）兼高[[機械|機械]]感度，在商業與軍事上並未得到廣泛應用。

作為一種不含[[氮元素|氮元素]]的[[爆炸物|爆炸物]]，TATP可以欺騙過時的[[安檢|安檢]]措施。TATP被認為曾用作多起[[黑社會|黑社會]]活動及[[恐怖襲擊|恐怖襲擊]]的[[爆炸物|爆炸物]]，如[[倫敦地鐵爆炸案|倫敦地鐵爆炸案]]<ref>{{cite web | last = Naughton | first = Philippe | name-list-format = vanc | date = 2005-07-15 | url = http://www.timesonline.co.uk/article/0,,22989-1695442,00.html | title = TATP is suicide bombers' weapon of choice | work = The Times (UK) | access-date =  | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080210235200/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/article/0,,22989-1695442,00.html | archivedate = 2008-02-10 }}</ref><ref name="Vince_2005">{{cite web | url = https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn7682-explosives-linked-to-london-bombings-identified/ | title = Explosives linked to London bombings identified | last = Vince | first = Gaia | name-list-format = vanc | date = 15 July 2005 | work = New Scientist | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | archive-date = 2016-04-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160413024418/https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn7682-explosives-linked-to-london-bombings-identified/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[2015年11月巴黎襲擊事件|2015年11月巴黎襲擊事件]]<ref name="nyt-isis">{{cite news | first1 = Rukmini | last1 = Callimachi | first2 = Alissa J. | last2 = Rubin | first3 = Laure | last3 = Fourquet | name-list-format = vanc | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/20/world/europe/a-view-of-isiss-evolution-in-new-details-of-paris-attacks.html | title = A View of ISIS’s Evolution in New Details of Paris Attacks | date = 2016-03-19 | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | archive-date = 2016-05-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160516003059/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/20/world/europe/a-view-of-isiss-evolution-in-new-details-of-paris-attacks.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>和[[2016年布鲁塞尔连环爆炸案|2016年布鲁塞尔连环爆炸案]]<ref name="url_LeVif.be">{{cite web | url = http://www.levif.be/actualite/belgique/la-mere-de-satan-ou-tatp-l-explosif-prefere-de-l-ei/article-normal-482065.html | title = "La mère de Satan" 